Key Match Events: Trent Alexander-Arnold scored a free kick to make it 2-0 for England
England's third goal was scored by Declan Rice from an Ollie Watkins cross
Post-Match Reflections: Lee Carsley was relieved to return to a more conventional style of play after the mayhem of the Wembley defeat against Greece
Miscellaneous Highlights: This was Jack Grealish's third start under Lee Carsley
Others: Harry Kane returned from injury to play as the number 9 for England
